* React is a open-source frontend javascript library which is used to build user interface specially for single page application
* React is introduced by facebook (Jordan Walker)


what are the features of react ?
    * It uses JSX which is xml like extension to the javascript
    * It uses Virtual DOM instead of real-DOM considering that real-DOM manipulation is expensive
    * it supports server-side rendering
    * Follows unidirectional dat flow or data binding i.e we can pass props from parent component to child component but not
        from child to parent